in the United States.

04:13.029 --> 04:15.562
It is a platform
that articulates

04:15.598 --> 04:17.430
what the solutions
can look like,

04:17.466 --> 04:19.733
so that we're able
to get to a place

04:19.769 --> 04:21.935
where police violence
is a thing of the past.

04:21.970 --> 04:24.437
<i>One of Campaign
Zero's biggest efforts</i>

04:24.472 --> 04:26.106
<i>is pulling statistics
on police killings</i>

04:26.141 --> 04:27.774
<i>from local news, social media,</i>

04:27.810 --> 04:29.542
<i>and national databases.</i>

04:29.577 --> 04:30.811
<i>They analyze the data</i>

04:30.846 --> 04:32.078
<i>to compare police departments</i>

04:32.114 --> 04:33.646
