to the erosion of trust

06:13.175 --> 06:15.209
between the community
and police officers.

06:15.244 --> 06:17.844
So, I think we have to look
at every case individually.

06:17.880 --> 06:21.114
The question is,
"Did they violate a law?"

06:21.149 --> 06:23.249
Because in that case,
what you just told me,

06:23.285 --> 06:28.121
